<#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell scrpt requires Windows to log when a process opens or manipulates a system object handle. This is important because:
Malware often interacts with system objects before escalating privileges
Handle access is a key forensic indicator of suspicious activity

.NOTES
    Author          : Susan Towett
    LinkedIn        : linkedin.com/in/stowett/
    GitHub          : github.com/stowett
    Date Created    : 2026-04-09
    Last Modified   : 2026-04-09
    Version         : 1.0
    CVEs            : N/A
    Plugin IDs      : N/A
    STIG-ID         : WN11-AU-000584
    Documentation   : https://stigaview.com/products/win11/v2r7/WN11-AU-000584/

.TESTED ON
    Date(s) Tested  : 
    Tested By       : 
    Systems Tested  : 
